@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_obrikt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.38 * v2 + 0.66) / (v0 + 0.96 * tmp + 0.73)) - wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.27)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.51)) / v2)
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs(v1))
    v1 = v2
    v2 = v1
    tmp = (0.04 / 0.59)
    v0 = (v1 * v1)
    v2 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
